g.text: Ian runs a research lab at UCL and is generally very busy. In addition to his research, he is also a lecturer to undergraduate students.​As some of his lecture is too hard to understand for student. Therefore, he wish there is a platform that help him to prepare teaching material. MotivationsProvide the undergraduates with high quality and easy to follow teaching materialsGoalsGet high-quality material for assisting his lectureEnsure that the material difficulty is not too hard to understand.Pain pointsStudent cannot follow his lectureAnswering questions manually takes too long Cannot find alternate instructional materialNameProf. Ian PattersonAge51RoleProfessor at UCL“I care about my undergrad students but cannot neglect my research” Behaviours
